{"tid":2339800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱被照眼 警誡無提  官：難信警說法 藏雷射筆男罪脫","createTime":"2020-12-25T02:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T05:00:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb795b0be4e8bde3b2bbe8ffc591c1cae4313d22","tid":2339800,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/7T3VX4J4UVBDTDJKO6H6MELFVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2F7T3VX4J4UVBDTDJKO6H6MELFVA%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=ea64b40f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201225%2F7T3VX4J4UVBDTDJKO6H6MELFVA%2F&h=6015f5f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201225/7T3VX4J4UVBDTDJKO6H6MELFVA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n稱被照眼 警誡無提 <br />\n官：難信警說法 藏雷射筆男罪脫<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年9月有人群凌晨聚集調景嶺港鐵站內，警員戒備期間拘捕一名工人，指他以雷射筆照射警員。涉案警員審訊時聲稱，由於被告在查問下不作回應，故他沒在警誡時指控被告射眼。裁判官屈麗雯昨裁決時強調，保持緘默是被告權利，反之執法人員有責任清楚提出指控，直斥案中警員作為專業執法人員，有此說法實在難以置信，裁定被告管有工具作非法用途罪名不成立。<span class=\"orange\">散庭後旁聽席上掌聲雷動</span>。<br />\n<br />\n被告。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SuiEWgOh8pshQPkQyJXckqS7fgE=/1206x983/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2WPZ5EXVNJANVDTN52DGCFMHPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSuiEWgOh8pshQPkQyJXckqS7fgE%3D%2F1206x983%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2WPZ5EXVNJANVDTN52DGCFMHPI.jpg&h=1da5b25e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員石家豪庭上多次改口，證供不獲接納。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方申充公證物遭駁回<br />\n<br />\n屈官引述片段指，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，屈官同時批評案中警員18146石家豪的證供。石早前供稱，當時他身處警車內，凌晨1時25分前一直看見被告。屈官指出，石觀看片段後，改稱1時25分前有時看不見被告，並多次更改關於警車位置的說法。此外，石在盤問下坦言，警誡時未曾向被告指出射眼一事，僅指控他射警車，<span class=\"orange\">解釋因被告保持緘默，他才會不作指控。屈官認為警員說法難以置信，「作為一個專業執法人員，不可能不知道有責任向被告清晰提出指控；被告是否回答，已是後話，這是他的權利」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n屈官又指，石於案發後四個月在案件主管要求下，才在證人供詞中加入被告射眼的指控。<span class=\"orange\">然而，當辯方問及主管的身份時，石自言不記得主管是男是女</span>、姓甚名誰。屈官認為說法不可信，同樣不接納石的證供。屈官亦質疑，控方沒有就更改案情提供解釋，做法不尋常，最終裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n控方在裁決後申請充公涉案雷射筆，指專家證人已證實涉案雷射筆可傷人體。屈官指雷射筆本身並非武器，控方亦無證據證明被告有非法意圖，駁回控方申請，將雷射筆交還被告。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTS3008/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-Uw25ydfs630krLITLi5XR4i45I=/664x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OCYKHFWODNAQTGM7OS3263Y3KY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-Uw25ydfs630krLITLi5XR4i45I%3D%2F664x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOCYKHFWODNAQTGM7OS3263Y3KY.jpg&h=7f221f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■裁判官屈麗雯強調，保持緘默是被告權利。"},{"pid":"6de8c99c77ee493247f4b62fd542215a44d44e57","tid":2339800,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"呢個官一時一樣"},{"pid":"13a98958d3b89ade9f569c1c311900ff3393d851","tid":2339800,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6de8c99c77ee493247f4b62fd542215a44d44e57","tid":2339800,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"呢個官一時一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"好過鄭紀航"},{"pid":"d61c85b2cb70c2e10d0d14ccfa62aee587dba3c4","tid":2339800,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13a98958d3b89ade9f569c1c311900ff3393d851","tid":2339800,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6de8c99c77ee493247f4b62fd542215a44d44e57","tid":2339800,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"呢個官一時一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"好過鄭紀航"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"姓鄭一路走來始終如一<img src=\"/