56d457c18f5ae56c8556","tid":2339800,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d94b5c0e1494f3a92ffb7d59e85b1880cb4447c","tid":2339800,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6de8c99c77ee493247f4b62fd542215a44d44e57","tid":2339800,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"呢個官一時一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:02:14.000Z","msg":"屈官一向都算正常"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:09:28.000Z","msg":"兩名案發時16歲的男女學生，去年11月在觀塘警署附近被截查，男生被搜出食用醋及消毒火酒，警方其後發現兩人在WhatsApp稱要用相關物品加害警員，兩人同被控串謀施用有害物品使人受損害、精神受創或惱怒罪。裁判官屈麗雯今（24日）於觀塘裁判法院處理女被告的判刑，指出女被告雖較遲認罪但有悔意，但接納她是年輕衝動犯案，因此同意感化官建議，判處她入更生中心。男被告早前亦已被判入更生中心。"},{"pid":"87fbe78011acd158c7598cd5e9e98fe2e89630d5","tid":2339800,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"屈官指雷射筆本身並非武器，控方亦無證據證明被告有非法意圖<br />\n但又咁多案例話係武器 仲係搞到我好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a7bccbd3b7887b112b9b41630555775c8fa9a4","tid":2339800,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"散庭後旁聽席上掌聲雷動。<br />\n<br />\n大家要去聲援呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefbb7a396501a413d4030a1713a2265cc9f73cb","tid":2339800,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c85274a18b78f297c39456d457c18f5ae56c8556","tid":2339800,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d94b5c0e1494f3a92ffb7d59e85b1880cb4447c","tid":2339800,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":